Description: Define your eyes with It's Me Kajal, the ultimate long-lasting, waterproof, and smudge-proof eye essential! With its intensely pigmented ultra-black formula, this kajal glides on effortlessly in one smooth stroke, delivering bold, high-impact definition. Enriched with nourishing ingredients, it keeps your eyes comfortable, making it ideal for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Whether you want a sharp, precise look or a sultry smoky effect, this kajal is your go-to for 24-hour drama and elegance.

24-Hour Long-Wear – Stays intact without smudging or fading.
Waterproof & Sweat-Resistant – Perfect for all-day wear, even in humid conditions.

Description: Say hello to luminous, high-shine lips that stay hydrated and vibrant all day long! It's Me Shine On All Day Long Lipstick combines rich, Matte color with a feather-light formula that feels as good as it looks. Whether you love soft nudes, classic reds, or bold hues, there’s a perfect shade for every mood and occasion!

Deep Hydration – Infused with moisturizing ingredients to keep lips soft & nourished.
High-Pigment, One-Swipe Color – Rich, vibrant shades that apply smoothly & evenly.
Non-Sticky & Lightweight – Silky, comfortable wear without any tackiness.
Versatile Wear – Wear alone for a glossy, radiant look or layer over matte lipstick for added shine.

Deep Hydration – Infused with moisturizing ingredients to keep lips soft & nourished.

Non-Sticky & Lightweight – Silky, comfortable wear without any tackiness.
Versatile Wear – Wear alone for a glossy, radiant look or layer over matte lipstick for added shine.

Description: Experience bold, long-lasting color with a hydrating matte finish that feels as good as it looks! It's Me Hydrating Matte Bullet Lipstick delivers full-coverage pigmentation in just one swipe while keeping your lips soft, nourished, and comfortable all day. Unlike traditional matte lipsticks that dry out your lips, our unique formula is infused with moisturizing ingredients to ensure a smooth, lightweight feel without cracking or flaking. Whether you love nude, pink, or red, there's a perfect shade for every mood and occasion!
Key benefits:
Rich, Velvety Matte Finish – Enjoy a true matte look with a soft, comfortable texture.
Hydrating & Non-Drying Formula – Infused with moisturizing agents for a smooth, supple feel.
Intense Color Payoff – One-swipe application delivers highly pigmented, long-lasting wear.
Lightweight & Non-Sticky – Feels like second skin, without any heaviness.
Perfect for Every Mood – A versatile shade range from subtle nudes to bold statement colors.
Ingredients: Polyethene Wax, Candeilla Wax, Ozokerite Wax, Shea Butter, Iso Propyl Mystriate, Polyisobutene, Isododecane, Octyl Methoxy-cinnamate, Silica, Hyaluronic Acid, Vitamin C, Niacinnamide, Fragrance, Additive May Containe, CI 42090/ CI 19140 / CI 77891/ CI 77499/ CI 77492/ CI 15850/ CI 175470/ CI 77681/ C1 177019
How to Use:
Apply directly onto clean, dry lips for a full-coverage matte look.
For a softer, diffused effect, dab gently with your fingertips.
To enhance wear time, prep lips with a light lip balm and use a liner before application.
Reapply as needed for fresh, long-lasting color.
Caution: Discontinue use if irritation occurs, FOR EXTERNAL USE ONLY

Tagline: NATURAL Formula for Stronger, Healthier Hair
Short description: Discover the power of Ayurveda with Aura Ayurvedic Hair Oil, a carefully crafted blend of 18 potent herbs and essential oils.
Description: Discover the power of Ayurveda with Aura Ayurvedic Hair Oil, a carefully crafted blend of 18 potent herbs and essential oils. Infused with Olive Oil, Coconut Oil, Brahmi, Neem, Fenugreek, and Black Cumin, this luxurious elixir deeply nourishes your scalp, strengthens hair roots, and stimulates natural hair growth. Say goodbye to hair fall, dryness, and dandruff, and welcome silky, voluminous locks with the goodness of nature.
Key benefits:
Reduces Hair Fall – Strengthens roots and prevents breakage
Promotes Hair Growth – Boosts circulation for thicker hair
Prevents Dandruff & Dryness – Deeply hydrates and purifies the scalp
Natural Shine & Smoothness – Restores lost moisture and enhances texture
Prevents Premature Graying – Protects hair from early aging with herbal nourishment
Ingredients: Almond Nut, Clitoria Ternatea (Butterfly Pea Flower), Butea Monosperma (Flame of the Forest), Rosa Damascena (Flower Rose Petals), Trigonella Foenum-Graecum (Methi Seeds), Abrus Precatorius (Red Sandal Pea), Vetiveria Zizanioides (Vetiver Root), Cocos Nucifera (Coconut Oil), Sesamum Indicum Oil (Sesame), Helianthus Annuus Oil (Sunflower), Azadirachta Indica Oil (Neem), Olea Europaea Oil (Olive), Argania Spinosa Oil (Argan), Bacopa Monnieri Oil (Brahmi), Nigella Sativa Oil (Black Cumin), Lawsonia Inermis Extract (Henna), Ocimum Sanctum Extract (Tulsi), Cymbopogon Citratus Extract (Lemongrass), Acacia Concinna Extract (Shikakai), Onion Extract (Lilum Cepa), Butylated Hydroxy Toluene, Fragrance.
How to Use:
Take a few drop of Aura 18 Herbs Hair Oil and warm it slightly.
Massage gently onto your scalp for 5-10 minutes in circular motions.
Leave it on for at least 2 hours or overnight for best results.
Wash off with a mild herbal shampoo.
